OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,FNew interim executive chairman Nathan
OL,7,FShi has addressed Wolves supporters
OL,8,Ffor the first time since arriving at
OL,9,FMolineux, acknowledging the club's
OL,10,Fdifficult position and promising that
OL,11,Ftrust will be rebuilt through action
OL,12,Frather than words.
OL,14,FIt follows the departure of Jeff Shi
OL,15,Fwho stepped down from his role as
OL,16,Fexecutive chairman of Wolves.
OL,18,FIn his role Nathan Shi will work
OL,19,Fclosely with technical director Matt
OL,20,FJackson, head coach Rob Edwards, and
OL,21,Fother members of the senior management.
