OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,FOn the pitch, it's not looking good
OL,7,Ffor Wolves, who are yet to a record a
OL,8,FPremier League win this season and
OL,9,Fhave just two points from their
OL,10,Fopening 17 games.
OL,12,FIn his message to the fans, Nathan Shi
OL,13,Frecognises Wolves' current situation.
OL,15,FHe said: "I recognise the current
OL,16,Fstrength of feeling among supporters
OL,17,Fcomes from your deep loyalty and pride
OL,18,Fin this club. Wolves means something
OL,19,Fspecial to this city and to its people.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/7
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
