OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,F"Frustration, criticism and emotion
OL,7,Freflect high standards and a genuine
OL,8,Fdesire to see the club succeed. I have
OL,9,Fheard you, and I know that trust has
OL,10,Fto be rebuilt through actions, not
OL,11,Fwords."
OL,13,FHe adds: "I want to start by
OL,14,Facknowledging where we are. The first
OL,15,Fhalf of this season has fallen well
OL,16,Fshort of our expectations.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/7
