OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,F"The results and performances have
OL,7,Fbeen disappointing, the situation is
OL,8,Fnot acceptable, and this has been
OL,9,Fpainful for everyone who cares about
OL,10,FWolves.
OL,12,F"As we work through this difficult
OL,13,Fperiod, I would like to ask for your
OL,14,Fsupport and patience, which I
OL,15,Funderstand is a huge ask after recent
OL,16,Fmonths.
