OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,F"My focus is on helping the club move
OL,7,Fforward with clarity and purpose,
OL,8,Fsupporting those responsible for
OL,9,Fdelivering change on the pitch and
OL,10,Facross the club, and ensuring everyone
OL,11,Fis aligned behind a clear direction.:
OL,13,FDefeat to Brentford on Saturday marked
OL,14,Fa tenth straight league loss for
OL,15,FWolves and a sixth since Rob Edwards
OL,16,Freplaced Vitor Pereira as Head Coach.
OL,18,FTheir next fixture is away to
OL,19,FLiverpool on Saturday 27 December,
OL,20,Fwith another away game, against
OL,21,FManchester United, three days later.
