OL,3,CNathan Shi vows action as Wolves
OL,4,Cendure winless Premier League start
OL,6,F"Our focus is on the club's
OL,7,Fsustainable development ` building a
OL,8,Fteam with a clear identity, belief,
OL,9,Fand a strong work ethic that
OL,10,Fsupporters can be proud of. We are
OL,11,Ffully committed to supporting the club
OL,12,Fas we navigate through current
OL,13,Fchallenges and look ahead to better
OL,14,Ftimes, that I am certain will come,
OL,15,Fwith time and hard work."
